---
title: Mild Chicken & Veggie Curry with Basmati Rice
description: There’s no need to call for takeaway when you can whip up this mild Indian curry with hardly any effort. It has a gentle creamy, tomato flavour that kids will love, with courgette and baby spinach to add essential greens. With tender chicken and fluffy rice, get ready to curry favour with the whole family!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b72625a30006c69e2346423-664cc86d.jpg
